DynamicAlerting

Class MPulseDataSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • DynamicAlerting.MPulseDataSet

  • public class MPulseDataSet
extends java.lang.Object
    If you pass in two strings (which are the JSON responses from two mPulse API queries), this class will parse them to create two datasets of pageGroups (called 'baseline' and 'test' dataset) and compare those two datasets to see if the test dataset is more than a certain baselineMultiplier above the baseline.
    Author:
    mikeostenberg
